universum.studios.android.intent

Class IntentStarters

  • java.lang.Object
    • universum.studios.android.intent.IntentStarters

  • public final class IntentStarters
extends Object
    Factory that may be used to create instances of IntentStarter for a desired intent context.

    Below are listed factory methods that provide standard intent starters:

    • activityStarter(Activity)
    • fragmentStarter(Fragment)
    • supportFragmentStarter(android.support.v4.app.Fragment)
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Martin Albedinsky
